title: Moderator/Support Team Fund
body: Our previous vote to buy 5 floor MC to stake and then fund the Mod/Support Teams is no longer necessary as the DAO can directly allocate $FISH to this group, cutting out a lot of unnecessary steps. The previously agreed upon $FISH was  approx. 700 $FISH every two weeks among the 30 (unless people are removed from roles due to inactivity), netting less than 23 $FISH per person as payment when adding in gas fees.
author: 0xa11435b21e0Eff08A6c2c5b8316ACC94054e8bAB
